01:58:02.940 --> 01:58:12.940
I'm, I'm, you have forged this partnership and a, as a, as a, quote, interracial couple since we have this concept of race that is defined.

01:58:12.940 --> 01:58:13.940
Yeah.

01:58:13.940 --> 01:58:14.940
Right.

01:58:14.940 --> 01:58:21.940
And I would invite your reflections on that experience too.

01:58:21.940 --> 01:58:25.940
I know, Priscilla, you had mentioned in the break that that was something that you wanted to touch on.

01:58:25.940 --> 01:58:34.940
Well, I did, I do remember what Dr. Dubois said.

01:58:34.940 --> 01:58:47.940
And it probably was after the loving, loving decision, loving versus Virginia, the, that overturned all the misage nation laws in the country.

01:58:47.940 --> 01:58:53.940
I think there were 17 states that still had misage nation laws.

01:58:53.940 --> 01:58:58.940
And he was a leader in the NAACP.

01:58:58.940 --> 01:59:14.940
And he, he made the statement that the NAACP did not support, it did not oppose interracial marriage and did not support interracial marriage.

01:59:14.940 --> 01:59:23.940
It believed that individuals who fall in love should have the right to pursue their relationships.

01:59:23.940 --> 01:59:26.940
And that's the way I felt about it.

01:59:26.940 --> 01:59:39.940
I mean, we didn't fall in love and get married and have three children in order to create some new racial grouping in this country.

01:59:39.940 --> 01:59:49.940
Some people talk about the elimination of race by consolidation or, you know, come on.

01:59:49.940 --> 01:59:54.940
We have to respect culture, cultural differences and so on.

01:59:54.940 --> 02:00:07.940
Our older daughter once told us that she thought the reason that we had such a long marriage was because of our moral compass.

02:00:07.940 --> 02:00:12.940
And that it, we came from very different backgrounds and so on.

02:00:12.940 --> 02:00:17.940
But somehow or rather we had the same goals.

02:00:17.940 --> 02:00:20.940
So there you go.

02:00:20.940 --> 02:00:22.940
How about that?

02:00:22.940 --> 02:00:25.940
That sounds very reasonable.

02:00:25.940 --> 02:00:30.940
Well, you might have come in for a little criticism of how to fight.

02:00:30.940 --> 02:00:35.940
