02:04:40.940 --> 02:04:48.940
And the economic impact on this country, just as same as we're seeing right now.

02:04:48.940 --> 02:04:56.940
So we have a poverty draft now and we have this country short-changing the needs of its own people.

02:04:56.940 --> 02:05:05.940
So Dr. King, I mean, listening to that speech this spring, I heard it again on the radio,

02:05:05.940 --> 02:05:11.940
which really made me happy. It was on our Albany Station NPR.

02:05:11.940 --> 02:05:16.940
It just, you know, really was so deep.

02:05:16.940 --> 02:05:24.940
And so he's been called a philosopher, what is an activist philosopher, Dr. King.

02:05:24.940 --> 02:05:29.940
And most philosophers are not sort of as activists, but he certainly was.

02:05:29.940 --> 02:05:36.940
Some people would maybe not call him a philosopher, but I would.

02:05:36.940 --> 02:05:40.940
And I also had great respect for Malcolm X.

02:05:40.940 --> 02:05:46.940
And we just recently went to the memorial of the author of the new book about him.

02:05:46.940 --> 02:05:54.940
And Manning Malibu, yes, he was, he's a family friend, not particularly close to us,

02:05:54.940 --> 02:05:57.940
but other members of family.

02:05:57.940 --> 02:06:08.940
And so, you know, this, I know in his speech, grassroots speech, you know,

02:06:08.940 --> 02:06:13.940
he ridiculed the March on Washington and so on. I could understand that.

02:06:13.940 --> 02:06:19.940
I could understand where he was coming from. It didn't make him my enemy for that.

02:06:19.940 --> 02:06:30.940
And I think he brought a lot of understanding to the, you know, the people of really disenfranchised in this country.

02:06:30.940 --> 02:06:36.940
So the combination of these two great leaders, we don't have that today.

02:06:36.940 --> 02:06:45.940
But what we really are missing is a mass movement that created them rather than that we need leaders,

02:06:45.940 --> 02:06:51.940
which we need the mass movement. We're not having it.

02:06:51.940 --> 02:06:57.940
Try as I may, I'm trying to get those seniors.

02:06:57.940 --> 02:06:59.940
Trying to get those in.

02:06:59.940 --> 02:07:04.940
So much so that I know, so much so about the music that you have been, recent years,

02:07:04.940 --> 02:07:11.940
been honored yet again for your ongoing commitments and contributions in these ways.

02:07:11.940 --> 02:07:20.940
