02:07:42.940 --> 02:07:44.940
Yeah. Yeah.

02:07:44.940 --> 02:07:47.940
It's just remarkable.

02:07:47.940 --> 02:07:55.940
You have forged this partnership as a, as a, as a, quote, interracial couple since we have this concept of race that has defined.

02:07:55.940 --> 02:07:58.940
Yeah. Right.

02:07:58.940 --> 02:08:03.940
And I would invite your reflections on that experience too.

02:08:03.940 --> 02:08:08.940
I know, Priscilla, you had mentioned in the break, but that was something that you wanted to touch on.

02:08:08.940 --> 02:08:16.940
Well, I did. I do remember what Dr. Dubois said.

02:08:16.940 --> 02:08:23.940
And it probably was after the loving, loving decision, loving versus Virginia,

02:08:23.940 --> 02:08:29.940
that overturned all the misage nation laws in the country.

02:08:29.940 --> 02:08:36.940
I think there were 17 states that still had misage nation laws.

02:08:36.940 --> 02:08:50.940
And he was a leader in the NAACP and he, he made the statement that the NAACP did not support,

02:08:50.940 --> 02:08:57.940
it did not oppose interracial marriage and it did not support interracial marriage.

02:08:57.940 --> 02:09:06.940
It believed that individuals who fall in love should have the right to pursue their relationships.

02:09:06.940 --> 02:09:19.940
And that's the way I felt about it. I mean, we didn't fall in love and get married and have three children in order to create some new racial groupings.

02:09:19.940 --> 02:09:32.940
So, grouping in this country, some people talk about the elimination of race by consolidation or, you know, come on.

02:09:32.940 --> 02:09:37.940
We have to respect cultural differences and so on.

02:09:37.940 --> 02:09:48.940
Our older daughter once told us that she thought the reason that we had such a long marriage was because of our moral compass.

02:09:48.940 --> 02:09:58.940
And that it, we came from very different backgrounds and so on, but somehow or rather we had the same goals.

02:09:58.940 --> 02:10:03.940
So there you go. How about that?

02:10:03.940 --> 02:10:06.940
That sounds very reasonable.

02:10:06.940 --> 02:10:12.940
Well, you might have come in for a little criticism of how to fight out.

02:10:12.940 --> 02:10:17.940
But of course, you're family as we have studied more about his family.

02:10:17.940 --> 02:10:25.940
There has been quite a lot of interracial relationship.

02:10:25.940 --> 02:10:33.940
Including the Alamo. I don't know quite figure that one out, but.

02:10:34.940 --> 02:10:42.940
Well, he has listed as one of, well, Paul and that is true.

02:10:42.940 --> 02:10:45.940
Yeah.

02:10:45.940 --> 02:10:55.940
Paul and Paul and that is son, but I don't know much about Paul and that, who was my great-great-grandmother.

02:10:55.940 --> 02:11:05.940
I don't know where she came from, but I was told that she came from a very wealthy family of the travestists around Richmond.

02:11:05.940 --> 02:11:10.940
So I hate to put her into the Richmond mat.

